<TEXT>
<P>
An unidentified man in his mid-20s jumped 200 feet to his death from the 
Interstate 805 bridge near Interstate 8 on Tuesday, said San Diego police. 
</P>
<P>
The suicide occurred shortly after 6 p.m. when the man parked his car on the 
southbound shoulder of the freeway just south of Interstate 8. The man jumped 
over the railing falling to his death in the 2800 block of Camino del Rio 
North. Identification is the man is pending. 
