</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
DEMONSTRATIONS -- GEORGIA; HANDICAPPED; COLLEGES -- GEORGIA 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100390-0088 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 286791 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 3, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 18; Column 5; National Desk 
</P>
