EMPLOYMENT; HIRING; JOB PROMOTIONS; LOS ANGELES -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES; 
EMPLOYEE RECRUITING; LOS ANGELS COUNTY -- GOVERNMENT EMPLOYEES 
</P>
