</P>
<P>
Age: 40 
</P>
<P>
Occupation: Incumbent; dermatologist 
</P>
<P>
Background: Served on the school board for the past nine years; helped to 
institute more rigorous graduation requirements, raising the percentage of 
college- bound students. 
</P>
<P>
